description: Spacious, updated 1 bedroom unit with courtyard view at the coveted 400 E Randolph building. The unit features an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas range, and tile floor, while hardwood flooring is present throughout the bedroom and living areas. Resort-like amenities include an indoor pool, hot tub, sauna, steam room, exercise area, half-court basketball, ping-pong, racquetball, child's playroom, hospitality room, business center, library, BBQ grills, sun deck, bike room, storage unit, 24/7 lobby desk. Some of Chicago's best amenities are just steps from your doorstep. Walk to the Loop, Millennium Park, Maggie Daley Park, Lakeshore East Park, Lakefront, Riverwalk, and Museums are all nearby. HOA includes high-speed internet, heat, A/C, gas, cable/TV, water and amenities. Parking is available for an additional $220/month. Ideal for first-time buyers or investors.
